        {
            "title": "參議員蒂利斯為川普的聯準會人選掃清道路,司法部撤銷對鮑威爾的調查",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/tL886VIzwoO3s9ZN2XI7DA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEB3R08Z_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 參議員湯姆·蒂利斯週日表示,他將撤銷對凱文·沃什出任<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"聯準會\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:聯準會;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/聯準會\">聯準會</a>主席提名的阻撓,這可能為沃什在現任聯準會主席傑羅姆·鮑威爾5月15日離任前迅速獲得確認鋪平道路。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這位北卡羅來納州共和黨參議員在NBC的《會見新聞界》節目中表示,在司法部於週五撤銷對鮑威爾涉嫌聯準會華盛頓總部成本超支的刑事調查後,他已準備好繼續推進,這是<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"蒂利斯\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:蒂利斯;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/蒂利斯\">蒂利斯</a>支持沃什提名所設定的唯一條件。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">蒂利斯表示:\"我已準備好推進沃什先生的確認程序,我認為他將成為一位出色的聯準會主席。\"</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-4062273c-034d-3a0c-b816-292a30ed6f0b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">\"我們非常明確地從司法部獲得了保證,我需要確保他們不會將司法部作為威脅聯準會獨立性的武器。因此,這將使沃什先生能夠按時推進其確認程序。\"</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">蒂利斯在參議院銀行委員會中握有關鍵一票,他的反對曾使該委員會陷入12比12的僵局,阻止了他本人支持的沃什進入參議院全體表決程序。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">聯邦檢察官珍妮·皮羅在聯邦法官阻止其辦公室向聯準會發出的傳票後改變了立場,儘管她在幾天前曾誓言要繼續推進調查。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8F%83%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E8%92%82%E5%88%A9%E6%96%AF%E7%82%BA%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E7%9A%84%E8%81%AF%E6%BA%96%E6%9C%83%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%B8%E6%8E%83%E6%B8%85%E9%81%93%E8%B7%AF-%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E9%83%A8%E6%92%A4%E9%8A%B7%E5%B0%8D%E9%AE%91%E5%A8%81%E7%88%BE%E7%9A%84%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-145824916.html",
